Follow [web/docs/admin-ux-architecture.md](web/docs/admin-ux-architecture.md) for:

- When to use full pages vs `DashboardEditPanel` vs modals vs popovers
- URL params `apanel` and `aid` (and legacy Fields `edit`)
- Closing panels must clear matching URL params; use helpers in `web/src/lib/admin/admin-panel-search-params.ts` and `useAdminPanelState` where appropriate
- Width tokens: `web/src/lib/admin/admin-drawer-classes.ts`

Before adding a new admin drawer, read the doc’s PR checklist.
